Title: Evicted!
Writer: Pendleton Ward (creator), Bert Youn, Sean Jimenez, Adam Muto (story), Timothy McKeon (staff writer)
Actors: Jeremy Shada, John DiMaggio, Olivia Olson, Erik Estrada
Plot: After Marceline the Vampire Queen visits Finn and Jake at their tree fort she informs them that she is moving in and kicking them out.
